data.description: Nestled in the serenity of a quiet cul-de-sac, your future home awaits! Step into the heart of the home, where the open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas. Kitchen features a convenient breakfast bar for casual meals and entertaining, a new stainless steel refrigerator, pantry, and laundry room. The split bedroom floor plan sets the stage for a versatile living experience, providing privacy and functionality for both residents and guests. Primary bedroom features ensuite with dual vanities, separate shower, oversized soaker tub, and walk-in closet. Venturing outdoors, you will find a fenced backyard providing a private escape that combines serenity with functionality. The storage shed, equipped with electricity, adds a touch of convenience, providing space for hobbies, tools, or a cozy retreat. Sugarmill Plantation amenities include a community pool, tennis courts, playground, and walking paths. New water heater; roof 2017. Call today for your private showing!
